{"tid":1964903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎 ‧ 水鏡八奇 ‧ 暗黑兵法】施永青：政府可宣佈所有租約完結　重簽租約","createTime":"2020-04-09T06:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T08:00:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e43dff177383f663a1be17be25d80868c425bdc7","tid":1964903,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200408/LRDA57M3PZEWLICV3TMVVE2FP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200408%2FLRDA57M3PZEWLICV3TMVVE2FP4%2F&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=520e0d18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200408%2FLRDA57M3PZEWLICV3TMVVE2FP4%2F&h=090b308f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200408/LRDA57M3PZEWLICV3TMVVE2FP4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/61W67Pjl3Fyva9WSUyQxfig6F7s=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/GIYOYT6AX5VPRNTVC2SOWZOFQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F61W67Pjl3Fyva9WSUyQxfig6F7s%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FGIYOYT6AX5VPRNTVC2SOWZOFQM.jpg&h=ac5f9954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中原集團創辦人施永青表示，正式屎橋，「幾個官員減薪做得啲咩」。<br />\n<br />\n港府宣佈第二輪抗疫措施，其中包括特首、司局長及特首辦主任未來12個月，將會減薪一成，以和市民共渡時艱。此外亦推行800億元保障員工就業計劃，只要僱主承諾不裁員，就會獲得薪金保障，所有為僱員提供強積金保障的僱主，都會獲得僱員一半薪金的補貼，最多9,000元。不過港府其實在3月時，已經按照薪酬調整機制，為所有公務員加薪，當中特首年薪，更增加12萬元至521萬元，為全球年薪第二高的地方首長。<br />\n<br />\n中原集團創辦人施永青指，主要官員減薪一年做法愚昧，形容是「正式屎橋」，「幾個官員減薪做得啲咩」，是一個討好選民和讀者的愚昧做法，因此並不贊成。反而港府實施半年僱主薪金保障，做法比預期好，原本以為港府只會施行數月，目前實行半年，加上一半薪金援助，同樣能保證基本收入，相信能幫助餐飲及零售業人員捱過疫情。<br />\n<br />\n此外，施永青認為疫情嚴重，政府可當作戰時狀態處理，宣佈所有租約正式完結，並讓所有租客與業主重新釐定租金，重簽租約，讓租金緊貼市況。如此一來，從租金乃至薪金方面協助各零售飲食企業，相信更能捱過疫情。施永青更強調，由於情況緊急，社會利益應該大於個人利益，應勒令各業主配合。更甚者，可以讓法庭暫停民事訴訟服務數月，就算租客不肯交租，業主也暫時無法從法律層面追討。<br />\n<br />\n記者:李嘉俊"},{"pid":"145e4ab9172d32fc344028ad17a4f022d418f924","tid":1964903,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:54:22.000Z","msg":"C老闆：我中原百9幾間鋪，重簽租約就fat fat"},{"pid":"fcd8b4dfa752e0dfc78bd3b87969c4feb656185f","tid":1964903,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更甚者，可以讓法庭暫停民事訴訟服務數月，就算租客不肯交租，業主也暫時無法從法律層面追討。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔駛暫停民事訴訟<br />\n<br />\n律師會餓死<br />\n<br />\n關閉土地審裁處就得"},{"pid":"47e79b534fcff6dab8b76d2b6507d15ed58f3484","tid":1964903,"uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"ＡＡ狗又想每張租約收佣金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4de88059d207a3047b13194f97c17c666ca640","tid":1964903,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"施永青馬克思主義戰士本性現形"},{"pid":"1f620104191b5a349596485dd5fca4a50a0a8346","tid":1964903,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f4de88059d207a3047b13194f97c17c666ca640","tid":1964903,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"施永青馬克思主義戰士本性現形"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"只要玩馬克思主義可以幫資本家賺到錢 / 慳到錢<br />\n<br />\n資本家也會講馬克思主義"},{"pid":"a1e4a8dc8d4b00ee3aa21d7748ae2e5981a3de7c","tid":1964903,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"短乜約<br />\n唔由間鋪吉啦？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4d3fe161b58483dd53d84f61b00d1db665700c","tid":1964903,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:15:55.000Z","msg":"可宣布一國兩